Package papplevaa.notepad.model

Class Tab

java.lang.Object
papplevaa.notepad.model.Tab
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Tab extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a tab in a notepad application that holds information about a document. Each tab can have a file path, title, last saved content, and current content. Implements the Serializable interface to support serialization.
